{"tid":1703941,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急!!! 貓貓情況極不樂觀(HELP)","createTime":"2019-11-10T13:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T10:50:43.000Z","uid":112549,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8594522b7ca223347220d23d782d6f19be5591db","tid":1703941,"uid":112549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T13:32:43.000Z","msg":"朋友冇連登AC 所以幫POST<br />\n貓貓去左睇醫生 但查黎查去都話仲未肯定到咩事 但我朋友就一直燒錢 到到無能為力 想請各位幫幫手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/htEnx0x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhtEnx0x.jpg&h=8e0fc190&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n聯絡電話:9202  0935<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDETAILS:<br />\n<br />\n11月7日貓貓全身冇力不能抬頭 軟趴係地下 <br />\n到去睇醫生左check右check都搵唔到確定成因或咩病 <br />\n只係照直講我唔明嘅數據，凝似貓腹炎，只知有機會48小時唔打針會死,打左有一半機會生存到.<br />\n照左x光 抽腹水 send去檢驗<br />\n當日同時個係fb群 搵人打左貓腹炎針 洗左2700蚊藥只夠三日 如果係完成療程要12周<br />\n<br />\n7號<br />\n即留院 check 9600$(等二星期先有報告）如貓腹炎48小時會死<br />\n加2700藥 僅夠三日份量<br />\n當天留院1000蚊一晚 ， 吊鹽水 檢查 藥物 服務 另計<br />\n<br />\n6號晚<br />\n返到去發現 全身軟哂冇力 不能抬頭 唔食野 只飲好少水 摸上去好冷 正常貓貓係暖 個晚我好驚醫院關左門 ，第二日未開門我就9點去到 因為冇book等到3點 。醫生咩都check但只話到比我知 凝似貓腹炎 FIP （極高機率致命）check一樣野都1000蚊以上 個日就用左差5多一萬蚊<br />\n醫生建議我搵FIP群搵到後義工門建議打左針先<br />\n個日我眼淚不停流 抱佢去醫院佢身好冷，第一次感受到強烈傷心感覺好怕佢就咁走左<br />\n<br />\n8號<br />\n探佢再打第二針  今日台到頭 肯食少少野  身都係好冷 摸佢成身都係骨 心好酸  2019年2月份兩兄弟一齊領養（佢地身世好慘 流浪過被義接收後絕育，但私人原因話限期前冇人要就放返出去 我唔忍心 就接返來）<br />\n<br />\n11月9日 <br />\n腹水腫脹 但我冇能力再比佢留到院接左返去 藥今晚我打完就冇啦 <br />\n天價住院費 藥理驗查費 藥物費 我己經負擔唔到，而家仲係未知佢確實病情<br />\n希望星期二再約見 醫院老闆 兩兄弟好乖 望主佢地咁慘 我冇能力幫到佢我覺得好失敗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E0DcaMU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE0DcaMU.jpg&h=61b0ca61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8FpVS0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8FpVS0f.jpg&h=0e8e621a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FrdGOyB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFrdGOyB.jpg&h=ba437678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R6YrZFg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR6YrZFg.jpg&h=ea4bc71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VXOLvMW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVXOLvMW.jpg&h=cc329816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AsSsJ6W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAsSsJ6W.jpg&h=2943daf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tkVaGTC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtkVaGTC.jpg&h=f99192c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9poPc0h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9poPc0h.jpg&h=df5d995a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fBfxVdD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfBfxVdD.jpg&h=67acc449&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f908cc11f7bd552b704b5054e016d590c846d26f","tid":1703941,"uid":16061,"like":2,"dislike":22,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T13:35:17.000Z","msg":"非洲都好多人生完養唔撚掂 你唔去幫?"},{"pid":"070448fa76fcd237b8ad713f7e18b4913d77521b","tid":1703941,"uid":112549,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T13:35:53.000Z","msg":"希望左家可以幫幫手 幫下貓貓"},{"pid":"13685c711291ab1c0486499bc9888c45d597cbfe","tid":1703941,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f908cc11f7bd552b704b5054e016d590c846d26f","tid":1703941,"uid":16061,"like":2,"dislike":22,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T13:35:17.000Z","msg":"非洲都好多人生完養唔撚掂 你唔去幫?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T13:38:01.000Z","msg":"比負皮個啲戇鳩仔記住捐多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9c56c003ff8550c1a71b70787af787f04aee67","tid":1703941,"uid":314830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"070448fa76fcd237b8ad713f7e18b4913d77521b","tid":1703941,"uid":112549,"like":0,"disli