dBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T14:03:30.000Z","msg":"原本個醫生話轉介去第二個醫生度 但佢話呢單case冇醫生肯接 其實連一個明確答案都冇 又唔知到底有咩方法去醫 真係好無助"},{"pid":"5fcda871a5839f79b2fb975b7825d81baac98bb8","tid":1703941,"uid":151419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:23:07.000Z","msg":"好慘！FIP真係好難醫，但最近見個朋友幫隻貓打針打返好。另外，都見人係fb開page 募捐搵人幫手醫佢自己隻貓，不如你都去貓貓page 睇下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006e505ca6033b068cc56da6c82657befc52c451","tid":1703941,"uid":299372,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e71803d4e00f0f50d8bae752afe01f745487b2f0","tid":1703941,"uid":201414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T13:43:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1703759/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1703759/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n貓&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;手足？？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做乜鳩姐你"},{"pid":"f35eec58d2d57e75583d4d64a04566df5522c655","tid":1703941,"uid":67005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:33:45.000Z","msg":"Facebook有FIP群啊！"},{"pid":"e0e4659edc4fabd498b98dde6c27a95c90d4753e","tid":1703941,"uid":265257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:39:48.000Z","msg":"我隻貓肝有事<br />\n睇咗2個醫生 驗咗幾次血 照咗超聲波同ct scan..留過一晚院 食咗2星期藥<br />\n<br />\n仲未check到究竟係發炎定有寄生蟲定cancer 已經洗咗2皮嘢<br />\n<br />\n動物有病睇醫生真係貴過人好多<br />\n樓主朋友加油"},{"pid":"72651ee337f68c748075e9bd3779c413b1583b82","tid":1703941,"uid":128489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:41:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eaa2bf3fff2c9538a8ca999163a3ec0c2dd70181","tid":1703941,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:46:03.000Z","msg":"隻貓食得好，室溫夠暖，訓得好，係你基本要做既野"},{"pid":"94758f1eac39a1b560f493b949fd2baf33846c47","tid":1703941,"uid":250995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:49:22.000Z","msg":"😿推 <br />\n集氣"},{"pid":"d386592f21c52a3459c0ccf2003bab014537f182","tid":1703941,"uid":79139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T16:53:00.000Z","msg":"聽日我wtsapp你朋友<br />\nFip你預用七八萬左右醫隻貓<br />\n叫佢度下經濟上支唔支持到"},{"pid":"82af01a10d5c18090160784b81f5069b51acd5ac","tid":1703941,"uid":280926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T17:29:27.000Z","msg":"就咁睇驗血報告未必100%係FIP (而事實以現今科技除咗解剖，根本冇測試可以100%肯定係FIP):<br />\n<br />\n1. AG (ALB:GLOB) ratio &lt;0.4 幾乎可以話90%以上中FIP，但你隻貓貓係0.63<br />\n<br />\n2. TP數值正常<br />\n<br />\n有冇做以下嘅嘢:<br />\n1. xray睇下有冇腹水<br />\n2. Send去化驗所驗PCR。千其唔好信診所驗嘅快速測試，癈嘅<br />\n3. 醫生有冇話你知嘅血清係咩顏色？<br />\n4. 有冇抽腹水驗？<br />\n5. 體溫正常？<br />\n<br />\n你宜家可以做嘅:<br />\n1. 保暖 (如果佢凍的話)，太凍唔會想食嘢<br />\n2. 少食多餐，盡量濕糧加暖水<br />\n3. 攞2nd opinion <br />\n<br />\n但老實講，如果真係濕性FIP，就真係冇藥醫到"},{"pid":"7efe7ef4c0fed074a37c6c20613da5b2a2ad5c5e","tid":1703941,"uid":248394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T10:50:43.000Z","msg":"推"}]}